properties.Description: Metadata describing a workbook template for an Azure resource.

priority.Description: Priority of the template. Determines which template to open when a workbook gallery is opened in viewer mode.

author.Description: Information about the author of the workbook template.

templateData.Description: Valid JSON object containing workbook template payload.

galleries.Description: Workbook galleries supported by the template.

localized.Description: Key value pair of localized gallery. Each key is the locale code of languages supported by the Azure portal.

name.Description: Name of the workbook template in the gallery.

type.Description: Type of workbook supported by the workbook template.

order.Description: Order of the template within the gallery.

resourceType.Description: Azure resource type supported by the gallery.

templateData.Description: Valid JSON object containing workbook template payload.

galleries.Description: Workbook galleries supported by the template.
